content:
Jianyu Wu is a Ph.D. Student of computer software and theory at the Open Source Software Data Analytics Lab, Peking University. Now, He is under the supervision of Prof. Minghui Zhou. His research interests include mining software engineering data, empirical software engineering and open source ecosystem.
武健宇, 北京大学信息科学技术学院计算机软件与理论专业一年级博士生(直博)，师从周明辉教授。他的研究兴趣主要包括软件工程数据挖掘，实证软件工程和开源生态系统。
